// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/DlKBz3 orthogonal circles iterate plant, 2023 jt
// 3d of https://www.shadertoy.com/view/DtVfR3 orthogonal circles flower sdf 2x
// related to https://www.shadertoy.com/view/dtGBDz orthogonal circles grassy plant

// Two iterations of https://www.shadertoy.com/view/clGBzm]orthogonal circles flower sdf 2
// 3d by rotational repetition.
// ALMOST exact: still error on boundary from base to first iteration.
// TODO: rotational repetition about roll axis of iteration case

// tags: sdf, flower, circle, distance, conformal, disk, loopless, orthogonal

